snippet.title: Yuvi Phan
snippet.description:
Hello my darlings♥️ My name is Yuvi and I'm a beauty blogger on a mission to help you look and feel amazing. In my channel, you will find makeup and fashion reviews, makeup tips and tricks, shopping hauls, and everything in between. Take a moment to look around and enjoy. Feel free to subscribe and drop comments with questions, review requests and share your tips. Thank you so much for reading. Let’s support one another for the love of beauty!
